$(document).ready(function(){

  $('#contact').bind('ajax:success', function(type, data, status, xhr){
	  var area = $('#contact-area');
	  if(area.html() == ''){
		  area.html(data);
	  }else{
		  area.html('');
	  }
  });

  $('#afp').bind('ajax:success', function(type, data, status, xhr){
